name: Based Manyu
description: Based Manyu is a meme token inspired by a real-life viral Shiba Inu named Manyu, who rose to global fame through high-production ASMR and spa-themed videos on platforms like TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, and YouTube. Known for his calm demeanor and pampered lifestyle, Manyu has amassed over 20 million followers and hundreds of millions of views. The token aims to bridge the world of meme culture and crypto by celebrating the cultural impact of this internet-famous dog. With a strong presence especially in Asia, the project stands out for its unique foundation in real-world virality and an already established fanbase.
